                    </div>
                    <div class="bio-section">
                        <h2 class="about-title">About the Human</h2>
                        <p class="bio-text">Hi, I'm Nicholas C. Zakas, an independent software developer, author, and coach living outside of Boston, Massachusetts. 
                            I've been a principal engineer at companies like Yahoo and Box. 
                            I created the <a href="https://eslint.org">ESLint</a> open source project and wrote several 
                            <a href="https://humanwhocodes.com/books">books</a>. Chronic illness forced me to leave the corporate world,
                            and now I focus on helping others through my writing, coaching, and open source work.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
